<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>GamingOnLinux 最新文章</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/</link><description>GamingOnLinux 的最新文章</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 13:21:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2023 年 GOG 夏季特卖中最后一款免费游戏是《Beholder 2》</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-final-free-game-in-the-gog-summer-sale-2023-is-beholder-2/</link><description>2023 年 GOG 夏季特卖期间，最后一款免费游戏将为您带来！您现在可以从 Warm Lamp Games 和 Alawar Premium 获得《Beholder 2》。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 13:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-final-free-game-in-the-gog-summer-sale-2023-is-beholder-2/</guid></item><item><title>Steam Deck 现已成为 Steam 全球销量第一</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-now-the-global-1-top-seller-on-steam/</link><description>随着 Steam 2023 年夏季特卖如火如荼地进行，加上 Steam Deck 的大幅折扣，它又重新登上了 Steam 排行榜的榜首。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 13:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-now-the-global-1-top-seller-on-steam/</guid></item><item><title>Wayland Wine 工作的第 4 部分现已合并</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/part-4-of-the-wine-work-for-wayland-is-now-merged/</link><description>为获得 Wayland 的全面支持而向 Wine 提交的一系列持续提交的第四部分已被合并。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 12:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/part-4-of-the-wine-work-for-wayland-is-now-merged/</guid></item><item><title>Valve 似乎禁止 Steam 上使用 AI 艺术的游戏（更新）</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/valve-appear-to-be-banning-games-with-ai-art-on-steam/</link><description>这是一篇关于 Steam 发布的有趣文章。由于法律领域的模糊性，Valve 似乎正在限制游戏中使用人工智能艺术。更新：Valve 发表了一份声明。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 08:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/valve-appear-to-be-banning-games-with-ai-art-on-steam/</guid></item><item><title>AMD RADV 获得有助于模拟和转换层的功能</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/amd-radv-gets-feature-to-help-emulation-and-translation-layers/</link><description>对于使用开源 RADV (Vulkan) Mesa 驱动程序的 AMD GPU 用户来说，有一些有趣的消息，因为它最近获得了对片段着色器互锁的支持。这对于仿真和翻译层很有用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 08:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/amd-radv-gets-feature-to-help-emulation-and-translation-layers/</guid></item><item><title>Steam 2023 年夏季特卖现已上线，Steam Deck 最高可享受 20% 的折扣</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-summer-sale-2023-is-live/</link><description>今天，2023 年 Steam 夏季特卖会再次上线，众多开发商为他们的游戏提供了大幅折扣。你知道演习吗？你的钱包已经躲起来了。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 17:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-summer-sale-2023-is-live/</guid></item><item><title>System76 为大家展示了“Nebula”全新 PC 机箱</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/system76-reveal-the-nebula-a-new-pc-case-for-everyone/</link><description>在通过定制 Thelio 台式机和 Launch 键盘建立了内部制造能力后，System76 现在正在扩展到适合所有人的 PC 机箱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 14:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/system76-reveal-the-nebula-a-new-pc-case-for-everyone/</guid></item><item><title>SHARGE Disk 可能是一个有用的 Steam Deck 存储助手</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-sharge-disk-could-be-a-useful-steam-deck-storage-sidekick/</link><description>我目前正在关注 SHARGE Disk，这是一个非常小的 M.2 NVMe SSD 外壳，可以直接插入 Steam Deck（以及许多其他设备）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 13:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-sharge-disk-could-be-a-useful-steam-deck-storage-sidekick/</guid></item><item><title>《Cassette Beasts》添加了新怪物、多人游戏和 DLC</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/cassette-beasts-adds-new-monsters-plus-multiplayer-and-dlc-coming/</link><description>《Cassette Beasts》无疑是今年最好的版本之一，也可能是现代最好的生物/怪物收集游戏之一。它还即将变大！</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 09:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/cassette-beasts-adds-new-monsters-plus-multiplayer-and-dlc-coming/</guid></item><item><title>用于配置 Corsair 键盘和鼠标的 ckb-next v0.6 现已推出</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/ckb-next-for-configuring-corsair-keyboards-and-mice-v06-out-now/</link><description>您拥有 Corsair 键盘或鼠标吗？那么你应该看看 ckb-next，它刚刚发布了一个新版本，支持更多新硬件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 09:29:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/ckb-next-for-configuring-corsair-keyboards-and-mice-v06-out-now/</guid></item><item><title>《矮人要塞》即将在 Steam 上发布 Linux 版本</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/dwarf-fortress-getting-close-to-a-linux-release-on-steam/</link><description>Bay 12 Games 和 Kitfox Games 的 Dwarf Fortress 刚刚进行了重大技术升级，听起来他们的 Native Linux 版本很快就会发布。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 09:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/dwarf-fortress-getting-close-to-a-linux-release-on-steam/</guid></item><item><title>为您提供的最新 Steam Deck 新闻摘要</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/a-round-up-of-recent-steam-deck-news-for-you/</link><description>时间很少吗？总是在旅途中？需要回顾一下最近的 Steam Deck 新闻吗？这里已经涵盖了您，快来解决您的小问题吧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 15:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/a-round-up-of-recent-steam-deck-news-for-you/</guid></item><item><title>Blender v3.6 现已作为新的长期支持版本发布</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/blender-v3-6-out-now-long-term-support-release/</link><description>Blender 3.6 版现已发布，它向许多公司展示了开源如何取得真正的成功，并且它是一个长期支持版本，因此最好升级并坚持使用它一段时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 14:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/blender-v3-6-out-now-long-term-support-release/</guid></item><item><title>《异形：黑暗后裔》是一款非常实时的 XCOM，我喜欢它</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/aliens-dark-descent-is-very-real-time-xcom-and-i-love-it/</link><description>最后，又一款让我热血沸腾的《外星人》游戏。我一直在玩《异形：黑暗后裔》，总的来说，我对这次体验非常满意。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 14:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/aliens-dark-descent-is-very-real-time-xcom-and-i-love-it/</guid></item><item><title>One Lonely Outpost 将在完整版本中获得 Linux 支持</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/one-lonely-outpost-to-get-linux-support-around-the-full-release/</link><description>在众筹活动结束后，开发人员经历了一些开发上的小问题，One Lonely Outpost 现已进入抢先体验阶段，并计划稍后提供 Linux 支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 12:56:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/one-lonely-outpost-to-get-linux-support-around-the-full-release/</guid></item><item><title>《行星生命》是一款外观简洁的独立沙盒进化模拟游戏</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/planetary-life-is-a-neat-looking-indie-sandbox-evolution-sim/</link><description>开发商 Sotenbox 最近发布了《行星生命》的预告片，这是一款看起来非常简洁的进化模拟游戏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 12:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/planetary-life-is-a-neat-looking-indie-sandbox-evolution-sim/</guid></item><item><title>itch.io 2023 年夏季精选捆绑包包含一些真正的独立精品</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-itchio-summer-selects-bundle-2023-has-some-real-indie-gems/</link><description>您还有机会玩一些甜蜜的游戏，同时还能节省您的钱。 itch.io 2023 年夏季精选捆绑包现已上线。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/the-itchio-summer-selects-bundle-2023-has-some-real-indie-gems/</guid></item><item><title>Proton Experimental 修复了《街头霸王 6》和其他游戏</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/proton-experimental-fixes-up-street-fighter-6-and-other-games/</link><description>对于 Steam Deck 和 Linux 桌面，Valve 发布了另一个 Proton Experimental 升级，重点是修复错误和回归。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 11:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/proton-experimental-fixes-up-street-fighter-6-and-other-games/</guid></item><item><title>开源主题医院游戏引擎 CorsixTH v0.67 获得首个 Beta 版</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/open-source-theme-hospital-game-engine-corsixth-v067-gets-a-first-beta/</link><description>噢，天哪，又再见空闲时间了。还记得经典的主题医院吗？ CorsixTH 是一个免费、开源和跨平台的游戏引擎，可使其在现代系统上保持良好的外观，并且新版本即将发布。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 13:28:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/open-source-theme-hospital-game-engine-corsixth-v067-gets-a-first-beta/</guid></item><item><title>Steam Deck 与 Starfield 的兼容性将在“稍后”讨论</title><link>https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-compatibility-with-starfield-to-be-discussed-later-down-the-road/</link><description>《Starfield》将于 9 月 6 日发布，显然有很多令人兴奋的事情，但它会在 Valve 的 Steam Deck 上运行吗？目前尚不清楚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 13:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.gamingonlinux.com/2023/06/steam-deck-compatibility-with-starfield-to-be-discussed-later-down-the-road/</guid></item></channel></rss>